4.title: NOVIO FANTASMA. ARACELI Y MISSAEL

episode of.title: Catfish Mexico: The TV Show (TV Series 2018– )

4.plot: Years ago Araceli fell in love with Missael, and started an online relationship, everything went very well, until she received a message where death was. Fortunately, everything was a lie and Misael reappeared.

imdb.plot outline: Catfish Mexico approaches the mystery and complexity of relationships in the digital world, trying to unmask the true identities behind false profiles on the Internet. To help people that travel through this path of mystery and drama, potential interested people are accompanied by YouTuber Chapu Garza, and the actor, musician and photographer José Luis Badalt. Catfish Mexico is the driving debut for both, who are more than ready to start.
